## âœ¨ Customization ideas
- Swap accent color in `:root --accent`.
- Add more tags/filters on `blog.html` and implement a simple `?tag=` filter.
- Add a `sitemap.xml` and `robots.txt` for SEO.

```
robots.txt
User-agent: *
Allow: /
Sitemap: https://<username>.github.io/<repo>/sitemap.xml
```

