## Minimal `sitemap.xml` (optional)
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">
  <url><loc>https://example.github.io/repo/index.html</loc></url>
  <url><loc>https://example.github.io/repo/blog.html</loc></url>
  <url><loc>https://example.github.io/repo/feed.html</loc></url>
  <url><loc>https://example.github.io/repo/about.html</loc></url>
  <url><loc>https://example.github.io/repo/contact.html</loc></url>
</urlset>
```

